data.description: This 4 bedroom 3 bath home sits on a wide lot in the desirable Chicago neighborhood of Norwood Park. Upon entering you are greeted  with beautiful hardwood flooring, a brick fireplace can lighting and lots of natural light shining thru this semi open floor plan.  The Living roomand dining room flow into the kitchen, featuring 42 inch maple cabinets all SS appliances, including a 5 burner stove with a double oven, gorgeous granite counter tops and a ceramic tile backsplash, a 4 seat breakfast bar area and still room to add a table in the breakfast area. The first floor also features a bedroom and a full bath. On  the 2nd level you will  find a large primary bedroom with a tray ceiling, nice  size closet enclosed with barn doors and an updated ensuite.   Two more bedrooms with a full bath are on the second level as well. all bedroom closets have Elfa  organizer systems.  The basement has a huge finished recreation/ family room, a laundry room, with steam technology washer/dryer storage and a utility room that has a door leading to the yard. Heated 2 car garage with storage, nice brick paved patio with a retractable awning for shade, the yard is fenced in with a western red cedar wood  fence. The yard is perfect for relaxing and entertaining.  Brand new concrete sidewalk in the backyard and under the porch. 200 amp service, updated copper water service, booster pump hi efficiency water heater dual zone furnace. roof, gutters, down spout air sealed attic blown in insulation in 1st floor and attic,  and vinyl siding (2015).Excellent Location! close to the 90 expressway, the Jefferson Park terminal, shopping and so much more.
